    <h1>DE&#xAD;TEN&#xAD;TION: THE SE&#xAD;RIES</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201029/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-10-29"><time>2020-10-29</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>Pre­mieres on Dec 5 on Net­flix</p>
    <p>Adapted from the Tai­wanese hor­ror ad­ven­ture video game of the same name, this Man­darin se­ries is set in 1990s Tai­wan. It fol­lows a high-school stu­dent Yun-hsiang, who un­know­ingly en­ters a for­bid­den area on cam­pus and en­coun­ters a ghost, Jui-hsin. The ghost slowly re­veals the dark and op­pres­sive history sur­round­ing the school dur­ing Tai­wan’s mar­tial law pe­riod (1949 to 1987).</p>
    <p>The se­ries is fronted by two new faces, Han Ning (left) in the role of Jui-hsin and Li Ling-wei in the role of Yun-hsiang.</p>

